snippet.title: NEW Flying Isles in Zelda BotW! | BotW + Islands Expansion Mod Reveal video
snippet.description:
"BRAND-NEW" Flying Isles in Zelda BotW! Reveal video

In this video can you see my newest mod! in the last few days i've worked on a mod that adds new flying isles to the sky of Hyrule, with new puzzles, new enemies and more new things to explore!
I'm planning to expand this mod with new Islands and maybe custom quests in future updates!

🍌 Gamebanana: https://gamebanana.com/members/1760638
🎲Download: https://gamebanana.com/mods/419652
